      "date": "2023-10-03 04:25:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> If the test is not passing, it is hard to know whether this patch is helping anything or not.\nI checked the parallel-scale-nfsv4 test result for patch set 1. Unmounting NFS clients passed.\n\n> In some respects, there is no urgency to land this patch if it doesn't improve the failure rate?\nAgreed. I'll rebase this patch on the fix for LU-17154.\n\n> It would appear that this patch is changing exactly the \"umount -f\" code that caused LU-17154 to fail?\nThe failure I reported in LU-17154 occurred on master branch without this patch.",
